summary: TL*THE CONTACT OWNS A 2000 MERCURY GRAND MARQUIS.  THE CONTACT STATED THAT THERE IS NO AIR CONDITIONING FILTER FOR THE AIR VENTS IN THE VEHICLE.  FORD STATED THAT THERE WAS NO VACUUM IN THE VENTILATION SYSTEM IN ORDER TO FILTER THE AIR CONDITIONING SYSTEM.  THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 46,000 AND CURRENT MILEAGE WAS 90,000.
